dct_title_s: Sketch of a route through part of Armenia and Asia Minor by James Brant Esqr., H.M. Consul at Erzrum
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Approximate territories of Ottoman pashaliks and of Georgia are shown. From: Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 6 (1836), pp. 187-223; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.6 1836.
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1836.
